<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>رسالة لأختي ❤️</title>

<style>
body{
    margin:0;
    height:100vh;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ffd1dc,#ffc0cb);
    overflow:hidden;
    font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif;
}

.container{
    text-align:center;
}

.envelope{
    width:300px;
    height:200px;
    background:#ff6fa5;
    position:relative;
    margin:auto;
    cursor:pointer;
    border-radius:10px;
    box-shadow:0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,.2);
}

.flap{
    position:absolute;
    top:0;
    left:0;
    width:0;
    height:0;
    border-left:150px solid transparent;
    border-right:150px solid transparent;
    border-top:100px solid #ff4f8b;
    transform-origin:top;
    transition:1s;
}

.letter{
    position:absolute;
    width:260px;
    height:160px;
    background:white;
    left:20px;
    top:20px;
    border-radius:10px;
    padding:15px;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    transform:translateY(80px);
    transition:1s;
    opacity:0;
}

.open .flap{
    transform:rotateX(180deg);
}

.open .letter{
    transform:translateY(-120px);
    opacity:1;
}

h2{
    color:#ff4081;
}

p{
    font-size:18px;
    line-height:1.8;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">
    <div class="envelope" onclick="openLetter()">
        <div class="flap"></div>

        <div class="letter">
            <h2>إلى أختي الغالية ❤️</h2>

            <p>
                حقك عليا لو زعلتك 🌹<br>
                إنتِ أغلى أخت في الدنيا كلها.<br>
                ربنا يخليكي ليا دايمًا 💖
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h3>اضغطي على الظرف 💌</h3>
</div>

<script>
function openLetter(){
    document.querySelector('.envelope').classList.toggle('open');
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
